private class StreamSpinClient.startUpLoadingScreen
extends com.google.gwt.user.client.ui.PopupPanel

Constructs a "loading screen" which is shown until the client gets an answer from StreamSpin. If the answer is empty, or corrupted, then makeMain will fail, and the login screen will be shown indefinitely
